ff 4If you attempt to play a floppy disk that does    
ff 4not contain a 'gcgame' folder, the system will    
ff 4copy a game template to the disk and then restart.
ff 4After the restart, the floppy disk will be        
ff 4playable and ready to edit.                  f     
ff 4                                                f  
ff 4Use the cmd "label set right 'diskname'" to name  
ff                                        4your games.
